2001-3265 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE ex rel. David LAPELL v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 2001-KH-3265. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Lapell, David; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Jefferson, 24th Judicial District Court Div. L, No. 95-1258; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, No. 01-KH-1175.

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.8; State ex rel. Glover v. State, 93-2330 (La.9/5/95), 660 So.2d 1189.
